      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That sounds good in theory but it's not how it feels. It feels like I'm just a constant source of stress and instability for them. I look at them and I just feel this overwhelming guilt that my presence in their lives is actually holding them back from being happy. It's like I'm a shadow hanging over everything they do.",
